latestIgtvVideos.title: Taj Mahal—Falguni Shane Couture Campaign
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Took 6 months of planning with the super geniuses @falgunipeacock and @shanepeacock and their relentless work with the authorities, they finally managed to get permissions to shoot at the legendary Taj Mahal Executing this shoot with 12 stunning models cast by @vahbizmehta with flawless hair and makeup by @mehakoberoi the team was working nonstop for 2 days on unadulterated passion and love. 
This whole shoot is a testament to our love—our love for couture, for the classic glamour it represents, and for the designers themselves, and the amount of time spent making each outfit all done with LOVE. 
Huge shoutout to @rupangisharma for managing this enormous lineup of models with me making it super efficient and easy. 
Special love to @errikosandreouphoto and @nirvairrai for capturing this flawlessly. 
Jewellery courtesy @narayanjewels 

#MRStyles #teammrstyles #stylefile #falgunishanepeacock #tajmahal
